==內容==
《藥業有心人》為大家介紹數家歷史悠久的香港中醫藥品牌之成功之道，同時將分析他們如何利用現代高科技，將中國傳統智慧延續下去。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkatv.com/zh-hk/atv-event/42756/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3-%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%96%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E7%82%BA%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602033253/http://www.hkatv.com/zh-hk/atv-event/42756/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3-%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%96%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E7%82%BA%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99 |archivedate=2015-06-02 }}</ref>

